    "This, effectively, gave us a set of 10 cases (considering Hong, et al. v. Block.One, et al. was included in the set twice).",
    "For full details of the charge selection process, see \"Appendix 6\".",
    "We drafted jury instructions for each of our violations to determine the criteria upon which our mock jurors would decide if the relevant violations were proven in the complaint.",
    "We aligned the jury instructions for each of the violations we studied very closely with jury instructions for the same charges in real cases.",
    "We based our jury instructions for the Securities Act violations on Dalton (2013) and Ninth Circuit Jury Instructions Committee (2023)."
